    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _CurrentLines.Array.size
      value: 11
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: You open the door and are greeted by a woman
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Tanghali na, kanina ka pa dapat gising. May sakit ka ba, Alex? Parang
        nakakita ka ng multo.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Sino ka? Nasaan ako?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: Si Tina, Tina Raymundo? Nandito ka sa bahay namin. Kailangan mo ba ng
        doktor?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: Raymundo?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: ' I looked around the kitchen outside where she stood. No wonder it
        felt a bit familiar, I was inside the Raymundo house, but it somehow feels
        off. Why does it look so new and lively?'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: "Then it clicked. Tina Raymundo\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[7]'
      value: THE Tina Raymundo, wife of Joe Raymundo, mother of the house is right
        in front of me.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[8]'
      value: Tina looks at me confused as I try to piece the puzzle together.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[9]'
      value: "Ah\u2026Aleks, siguro pagod ka pa galing sa biyahe, Hayaan muna kita,
        kailangan ko pa asikasuhin mga anak ko. Baba ka nalang kung may kailangan
        ka. Sana makikilala mo din sila ngayong bakasyon."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _CurrentSpeakers.Array.size
      value: 11
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[10]'
      value: Once she left I returned inside the bedroom
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentSpeakers.Array.data[0]'
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
